{"tid":2394296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥：建議立法將「起底」列刑事罪行","createTime":"2021-02-04T05:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T07:35:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cc50e917296ae6604f4c0b60b9b3f4285c3bfb04","tid":2394296,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今（4日）到立法會出席答問大會，她提及將會在今個立法年度就5大政策提交條例草案，包括立法訂明區議員須宣誓、引入非本地醫生、制定劏房租務管制、加強舊式樓宇消防安全，以及打擊虛假信息、侵犯個人私隱、擾亂社會秩序等行為，其中建議將「起底」定為刑事罪行。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，立法打擊各類侵犯個人私隱、散播仇恨及歧視性言論、虛假信息、擾亂社會秩序等行為，她稱由於議題牽涉廣泛及具一定敏感性，將研究其他國家及地方的經驗及處理方法，先處理最迫切的「起底」行為，將從執法、立法兩方面入手，把「起底」行為定為刑事罪行。"},{"pid":"7de57b47385cf021c03e9613128717d145ae75a6","tid":2394296,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0359f08f5e301cff3dd1ec3cf0cfefb12b79790e","tid":2394296,"uid":63543,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"配合埋選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a34b227aed90ece948e28eb4fbdc76667e31c0a","tid":2394296,"uid":264245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"黨軍公開人私隱就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c8fd83b5d59352823099f5d1af0ab55b292127","tid":2394296,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0359f08f5e301cff3dd1ec3cf0cfefb12b79790e","tid":2394296,"uid":63543,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"配合埋選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7439910846ac16cb4c5103fd364699e507743b","tid":